data.description: Come see this home that has so much potential. You could be centrally located in Meridian for under $375K. Enjoy easy commutes, and be 10 minutes from everywhere. It has plenty of storage in the back with 2 sheds, a chicken coop, and raised garden beds for the hobby farmer. It has original hardwood floors, newer HVAC and roof. The big ticket items have been taken care of for you, this home just needs your personal touches. All with no HOA to get in your way!
